[preface]
== Preface by Mybrid Wonderful

Welcome to the wonderful world of words!
Welcome to New Democracy, of the people, by the people, and for the people and everything else is new!
The Irreni Social edition of New Democracy is an additional brand of Irreni World Scale.
Irreni World Scale(tm) (Irreni) is a project hosted on the Irreni Social website at: https://irreni.social/
Irreni is a form of mesh society that replaces hierarchy with mesh.


New Democracy is of the people. In this case it means the book is in the public domain, freely copied and expanded on. Everyone is encouraged to make New Democracy their own. Everyone is write their specific edition where this is the Irreni World Scale edition using your specific branding. You are free to brand your version and sell it. However, in the spirit of New Democracy being for the people then it is recommended to make all editions free to copy.

This book is intended for everyone on planet Earth. This is not an academic text verse at the university level.

This book can be used as a buffet where you take want you want and skip the rest. However, it is recommended that everyone expand on the ideas initially until one can understand the full picture.

I believe happy people can create happy environments and unhappy people cannot. Therefore this book has cooking recipes and other life goodies to make this endeavor happy. Also, not a text book. :)

The origin of New Democracy is that it began around 1980 when I turned the age of eighteen. I had just graduated high school. I started reading early American history as a hobby with a keen eye towards the circumstances surrounding so many keen minds and huge egos working together to found the United States. Also, I am neurodivergent and started research into psychology and culture to better understand how to fit into this world.

In 1980 Ronald Reagan became President. During Reagan's administration I was comparing the state of US Democracy to how it was originally intended and came to the conclusion that the experiment had already failed. I then started collecting books and designing what eventually became Irreni World Scale.

I was raised Christian going to a Wesleyan Methodist church. My mother used the free bus offered for Sunday services as free baby sitting for a few hours on Sunday. I attended weekly until about the age of fourteen. I cannot ever remember believing what I was told, always considering Christianity to be nonsense. Even as a child I would come up with better social designs than that which is offered by Christianity. It is fair to say I became obsessed with social engineering as an aspect of my being neurodivergent and have been obsessed ever since.

This is a happy book and not an anti-religious book. Religion is ignored in this book except to state that Irreni makes no special concessions for religion and therefore it is ignored.

My formal education and occupation is software engineering because social engineering is not an occupation.

I hope you enjoy the book! I hope you make New Democracy your own in whatever form that may take. I especially hope that you will join an MGO, or micro-governing organization. The MGO is a mesh node that makes up the mesh, the fabric of New Democracy.

Cheers!